### =====================
### GET REQUESTS
### =====================

### Get all games (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/games
Accept: application/json

### Get all games - Page 1 with 3 items
GET {{baseUrl}}/games?page=1&pageSize=3
Accept: application/json

### Get all games - Filter by genre
GET {{baseUrl}}/games?genre=Football
Accept: application/json

### Get all games - Filter by price range
GET {{baseUrl}}/games?minPrice=40&maxPrice=60
Accept: application/json

### Get all games - Sort by price descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/games?sortBy=price&descending=true
Accept: application/json

### Get all games - Combined filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/games?genre=Football&sortBy=price&descending=true&page=1&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

### Get a single game by ID (replace with actual MongoDB ObjectId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Accept: application/json

